text: Kun Hai Shop, a growing Chinese supermarket with two outlets in Singapore, offers over 10,000 Chinese snacks, beverages, and pantry staples, both in-store and online via Shopee. The Clementi Mall outlet has a decent selection for its size at reasonable prices, including some hard-to-find items. Though the store is a bit packed and messy, it’s a convenient spot for affordable and authentic Chinese food products.
Interesting products not available at Scarlett Supermarket. They sell freshly made 煎饼果子！The ice cream is a deal at 80 cents!
